  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Le Bistro Restaurant is an excellent fusion of local tradition and international cuisine and boast a large selection of wine. Diners can enjoy lovely views as the restaurant overlooks the main promenade with the beach beyond. A continental buffet breakfast is served each morning offering fresh fruits, cereal, pastries, cakes, juices, tea and coffee. Half and full board options are available for a supplement. </p>
<p>The hotel has its very own cocktail bar serving up delicious combinations for guests to try.</p>
<p>The lounge bar is open for aperitifs and from mid June to the end of October, one night a week you’ll find live music playing.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
