  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Pool &amp; Beach</u></strong></p>
<p>The hotel has a large (50m²) swimming pool that is heated to 28°C and surrounded by sun loungers. The pool is open from mid May to the end of September.</p>
<p>You can enjoy the beach facilities including sun loungers from the 3<sup>rd</sup> row which are included in the hotel price from the 25 May – 20 Sep.</p>
<p><strong><u>Spa</u></strong></p>
<p>The hotel boasts the largest spa in Riccione. It has an indoor pool, Jacuzzi, Salt room, Sauna, Turkish bath, showers as well as massage and treatment rooms. Entrance to the spa, massages and treatments are payable locally. Please note that guests must be 16 or over to use the spa facilities.</p>
<p>Open Monday-Sunday 10am to 9pm &amp; Friday from 10am to 12am.</p>
<p><strong><u>General Facilities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Miniclub runs from the 10 Jun – 10 Sep for children aged 3-12 six days a week.</li>
<li>Free bike rental</li>
<li>Garage (payable locally approx. €10 per day)</li>
<li>Free outdoor parking (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
<li>TV room</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
