  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is a great modern hotel with a fab location beside Riccione's beachfront promenade. They've got a section of the beach reserved for guests so grab a lounger and get some sunbathing in. There's also a lovely heated outdoor pool at the back of the hotel in the garden. It's in the centre of Riccione with lots of bars and restaurants within walking distance. You can also get to the train station easily and explore further afield.</p>]]></listingDescription>
