  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>are about 16m² and have a balcony. These rooms sleep two people and come with air conditioning, heating, safe, hairdryer, minibar and telephone.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are about 18m² and have a balcony with side sea views. These rooms sleep two to three people. Baby cots are available on request (approx. €15 per night)</p>
<p><strong>Family Superior Rooms </strong>are about 18m² and have a balcony with side sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Prestige Rooms</strong> are slightly more spacious at about 19m². These rooms have balconies with front sea views and can sleep up to four people with a maximum of three adults and one child. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Singe Occupancy </strong>available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
